title: Final victims pulled from rubble in Florida bridge collapse
text:
Final victims pulled from rubble in Florida bridge collapse Sunday, March 18, 2018 - 01:16 
Police say they have recovered the sixth and final victim from beneath the rubble in the Florida bridge collapse. Linda So reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
